FBIS4-16020 "drsov071_u_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-071 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 Latvia Riga Awaits Repeal of Russian Decision on Bases Riga Awaits Repeal of Russian Decision on Bases LD1304062594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0426 GMT 13 Apr 94 LD1304062594 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Riga April 13 ITAR-TASS -- Negotiations between Riga and Moscow will not resume unless Russia repeals Boris Yeltsin's order to create military basis on the territory of Latvia, Prime Minister Valdis Birkavs announced on Tuesday night. He said all opportunities must be used to achieve more favourable conditions for the signing of an accord between the two countries. Birkavs expressed hope that foreign investors would help repatriate retired Russian servicemen. The prime ministers of Latvia and Estonia will discuss their common stand on the these issues at the forthcoming meeting on Friday.
